\mu(t) = \mu_0 e^{\gamma t}

Damage accumulation model:
\frac{dD}{dt} = \alpha - \beta R(t), \quad R(t) = R_0 e^{-\gamma t}

Neural scaling law:
L(N) \propto N^{-\alpha}, \quad \alpha \approx 0.05\text{--}0.1

Moore's law:
N_{\text{transistors}}(t) = N_0 \cdot 2^{(t - t_0)/\tau}, \quad \tau \approx 2 \text{ years}

